OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fnight with clear spells at first. Some
OL,7,Fcloud will spread across from the west
OL,8,Fovernight giving the odd light shower
OL,9,Fin places. Skies clearing in the west
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start in the east
OL,13,Fwith the odd shower but soon
OL,14,Fbrightening up. Otherwise it will be a
OL,15,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
